KEVIN DRUMM

              —
              Double The Room
            
              (Boomkat Editions | Documenting Sound)
label: Boomkat Editions | Documenting Sound
description:
Kevin Drumm takes us to the precipice of loss and melancholy on this stark 8th instalment in our Documenting Sound series. Fuelled by feelings of saudade and isolation, Drumm takes the concept of field recordings to a different place; asking someone else to record their life -  so that he can re-construct.

On one side: Drumm recording at home, on his own... more

title_full:
LUC FERRARI

              —
              Labyrinthe de Violence
            
              (Alga Marghen)
label: Alga Marghen
description:
For the first time on vinyl, a momentous 1975 installation soundtrack by the poet of musique concrète surfaces in its entirety, presenting 82 mins of music that remarkably foreshadows myriad styles of cut-up collage, noise, industrial scaping and power electronics.

Containing the four soundtracks realised for an A/V multimedia performance at the Galiéra... more
